Text: Heard good things about this... Thanks
Am I the only one to notice that this is really s07e04? Also where is the real episode 3 its driving me nuts.

This is S07E04..."Eggball"  The real S07E03 is uploaded as S07E02, and as far as I can tell all of the other ones uploaded by this person are the same way.  They must've skipped ep01 because it aired in December and ep02 didn't air until February.  If you get confused when downloading, I would recommending going to wikipedia and looking at the episode guide there to figure out which one is which (they have short descriptions) because for whatever reason imdb doesn't even have all of the episodes up yet and there's no descriptions available.
